main event: A UFO sighting reported in Menlo Park, California on September 7, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting involved a single round cylindrical object emitting bright white light., The object was observed for a few seconds at a straight level trajectory., The observation was made from the ground by civilian witnesses., There were no photographs or physical evidence of the sighting., The report is part of Project Blue Book documentation.
sighted object: one round cylindrical object emitting bright white light
